title: Police College team crowned champions
content: Under the patronage and in the presence of Lieutenant General Ghanem bin Shaheen al-Ghanem, Chief of Staff of the Qatar Armed Forces, the Police College team was crowned champions of the 2018 Ramadan ..  Read on the original site
